data.description: Nestled in the coveted Point Defiance neighborhood, your warm and inviting home awaits! The main floor boasts hardwoods in the entry and kitchen and is very light and bright. Open floor plan with formal living & dining rooms, family room w/gas fireplace, office, and mudroom offer flexibility. Beautiful kitchen with breakfast bar, stainless, granite, and pantry. Upstairs, the primary suite, with 5-piece and walk-in closet, bonus room with balcony, and two bedrooms provide comfortable retreats. The large balcony off the primary and bonus room are a perfect for savoring the views. Enjoy outdoor living with a covered patio, front porch, and Mountain and Sound views. Easy walk to Pt Defiance and Ruston. This is North Tacoma living at its finest!
